# Defensive deny-all allowlist (review findings 8 and 12).
# Ignore everything by default, then re-include ONLY the publishable site files.
# Dotfiles are matched by "*" too, so they must be re-included explicitly.
*

!.gitignore
!.nojekyll
!index.html
!whangarei_map.html
!whangarei_table.html
!whangarei_daycare_table.html

# whangarei_data.js is intentionally NOT included: the data is inlined into each
# page, so the external file is optional (open question still pending). If kept,
# add: !whangarei_data.js
